%% Activity - Tìm tuyến

flowchart TD
  Start((Start)) --> Input["User enters origin/destination or clicks on map"]
  Input --> Geocode{"Is input geographic?"}
  Geocode -- No --> CallGeocode["Call geocoding service"]
  CallGeocode --> FindRoutes["Query routes via DB/GIS\n(filter by proximity, service) "]
  Geocode -- Yes --> FindRoutes
  FindRoutes --> Rank["Rank/score candidate routes"]
  Rank --> Display["Return results to frontend (map + list)"]
  Display --> End((End))
